@startuml
autonumber
actor "Backoffice Operator/Admin" as BO
participant "AircraftModelController" as Ctrl
participant "GetTopUtilizedModelsUseCase" as UC
participant "AircraftRepository" as Repo
database "Database" as DB

BO -> Ctrl : GET /api/aircraft-models/top-utilized?sortBy=hours
activate Ctrl

Ctrl -> UC : execute("hours")
activate UC

UC -> Repo : findAll()
activate Repo

Repo -> DB : SELECT * FROM aircrafts
activate DB
DB --> Repo : list of all aircraft instances
deactivate DB

Repo --> UC : List<Aircraft>
deactivate Repo

note right of UC: Groups aircrafts by model.\nSums totalFlightHours and\nnumberOfAssignments per model.\nSorts by chosen criteria DESC.\nLimits to 5 entries.

UC -> UC : map to TopUtilizedModelResponse

UC --> Ctrl : List<TopUtilizedModelResponse>
deactivate UC

Ctrl --> BO : 200 OK (JSON Collection)
deactivate Ctrl
@enduml